OL,3,CMinisters will be told to use AI to
OL,4,Cscreen migrants for threats, adviser
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMinisters will be recommended to use
OL,8,Flive AI facial recognition to screen
OL,9,Fmigrants arriving in the UK for
OL,10,Fthreats, the Government's anti-terror
OL,11,Flaw adviser has said.
OL,13,FJonathan Hall KC, the UK's independent
OL,14,Freviewer of terrorism legislation, has
OL,15,Fsaid he will recommend the Government
OL,16,Fintroduces the technology at migrant
OL,17,Fprocessing facilities in Kent when he
OL,18,Fpresents his annual report this year.
