OL,3,CMinisters will be told to use AI to
OL,4,Cscreen migrants for threats, adviser
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe move would allow border officers
OL,8,Fto screen those crossing in small
OL,9,Fboats against a database of terror
OL,10,Fsuspects.
OL,12,FIn an interview with LBC, Mr Hall also
OL,13,Fwarned that Manston, the migrant
OL,14,Fprocessing centre where those on small
OL,15,Fboat are detained after arrival in the
OL,16,FUK, had at one point become "so
OL,17,Foverwhelmed that people had to be
OL,18,Freleased before all the checks had
OL,19,Fbeen done".
