OL,3,CMinisters will be told to use AI to
OL,4,Cscreen migrants for threats, adviser
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe reviewer told the broadcaster he
OL,8,Fvisited Western Jet Foil in Dover last
OL,9,Fyear, the initial processing site for
OL,10,Fmigrants, as well as the Manston camp.
OL,12,F"At the time I was there, it was lots
OL,13,Fof sort of tents and more permanent
OL,14,Fstructures," he said.
