OL,3,CMinisters will be told to use AI to
OL,4,Cscreen migrants for threats, adviser
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"The tricky thing with that is that a
OL,8,Flot of people can suddenly arrive on
OL,9,Fone day, and if lots arrive on one
OL,10,Fday, how are counterterrorism police
OL,11,Fgoing to have the opportunity to
OL,12,Fscreen them? And this is the really
OL,13,Fdifficult bit.
OL,15,F"They can't be kept, quite rightly, in
OL,16,Finhumane conditions, which means that
OL,17,Fif you're jamming everyone into a
OL,18,Ftent, they can stay only there for a
OL,19,Fday."
