OL,3,CMinisters will be told to use AI to
OL,4,Cscreen migrants for threats, adviser
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FBut with migrants being moved out,
OL,8,Fthis meant there was not the
OL,9,Fopportunity to screen them, Mr Hall
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FHe added: "It's going to be published
OL,13,Fin a few weeks, but in my report, I'm
OL,14,Fgoing to say that, use live facial
OL,15,Frecognition at Western Jet Foil, so
OL,16,Fwhen people get off the boat, they can
OL,17,Fbe screened, and if they've got a
OL,18,Fwatch list of people coming in, they
OL,19,Fwill know there and then that they're
OL,20,Fdealing with someone who is on a watch
OL,21,Flist."
