OL,3,CMinisters will be told to use AI to
OL,4,Cscreen migrants for threats, adviser
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Hall said this would allow migrants
OL,8,Fto be checked against a "database of
OL,9,Fimages of people who are suspicious,
OL,10,Fwho are potential terrorists".
OL,12,FThe situation off the Dover coast was
OL,13,F"really complex" and evolving, he
OL,14,Fsaid, with border staff unable to
OL,15,Fanticipate the surges of people
OL,16,Fcrossing the Channel.
OL,18,F"At one stage, they were so
OL,19,Foverwhelmed that people had to be
OL,20,Freleased before all the checks had
OL,21,Fbeen done," he said.
