OL,3,CMinisters will be told to use AI to
OL,4,Cscreen migrants for threats, adviser
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThis meant they were released "without
OL,8,Fthe full amount of checks", Mr Hall
OL,9,Ftold LBC, adding border officers had
OL,10,Fto strike a balance between screening
OL,11,Fand ensuring arrivals were not kept in
OL,12,F"potentially inhumane conditions".
OL,14,FMore than 6,200 people have crossed
OL,15,Fthe English Channel since the start of
OL,16,Fthe year, higher than in the same
OL,17,Fperiod in both 2023 and 2022.
OL,19,FRishi Sunak has made "stopping the
OL,20,Fboats" one of his key leadership
OL,21,Fpledges as Prime Minister.
